   SIDNEY-SLAYINGS _ DAYTON, Ohio _ Thursday night's horror seems
impossibly incongruous with the sense of well-being, of order, that
permeates small Sidney, named an All-American City in 1964. A look
at how the killings of three teen girls there has impacted the
town. (McCarty, Dayton Daily News) MOVED
