<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-11 18:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6083 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-lopezcolumn-HNS &LR;      07-11 2178
