<P>
   DROP-SOUTH POLE (Undated) _ An exhausted but jubilant C-141B
Starlifter aircrew from McChord Air Force Base in Washington state
reported success early Sunday after an emergency operation to
airdrop medical supplies at the South Pole for a scientist
diagnosed with breast cancer.
