   HDTV-STANDARDS (Washington) _ Sinclair Broadcasting, which
controls more television stations than any other industry player,
has embarked on a crusade to have the FCC revisit the technical
standard for digital television _ even as stations around the
country have begun installing equipment and consumers have begun
buying TV sets based on that standard. By Joel Brinkley.
