   VODKA-AD-COLUMN (New York) _ The Advertising Column: There's an
old saying that nothing rhymes with ``orange.'' So there may not be
a rhyme for a multimillion-dollar campaign to pitch a new
orange-flavored variety of Absolut vodka _ but there certainly is a
